text:
Highland Park (Queens-Brooklyn):  Shown are several early views of the park, part of which is in Queens and part in Brooklyn.

Views 1 and 2 show the Ridgewood Reservoir, picnic grounds and National Cemetery (view 2).  The reservoir is in Queens; the cemetery in Brooklyn.

View 3 shows the fence around the reservoir and the Interborough Parkway (left).

Wilberforce Eames Collection     1916
Views 1-4
title: Brooklyn: Highland Park.
